<ab facs="#facs_473_r2l11"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc das haben wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_473_r2l12">daʒ wır <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>guldin<ex>n</ex></expan> in <expan>lang<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒeıt bey vns nıht haben <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſuchen</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_473_r2l13"><expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ſo <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan> wır auch niht / daʒ ʒu dıſen <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> ıcht vıl neẅer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_473_r2l14"><expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> bey vns geen / daʒ wır eẅch <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> dauon niht <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>ſchreıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
