<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        habt von der <expan>guldin<ex>n</ex></expan> müncz
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das haben wir wol
                                <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        ewr <expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir <expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>guldin<ex>n</ex></expan> in <expan>lang<ex>er</ex></expan> zeit bey
                        uns niht haben <expan>v<ex>er</ex>suchen</expan>
<expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>. So <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan> wir auch
                        niht, daz zu disen <expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> icht vil newer
                                <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> bey uns geen, daz wir ewch
                                <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> davon niht
                            <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> zu <expan>schreibe<ex>n</ex></expan>.
                        Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Petri et Pauli.</ab>
</div>
